content: That sounds like an amazing itinerary! I'm really excited about the scenic routes and bike-friendly stops. Since I'll have four bikes with me, I'll make sure to book the accommodations with bike storage in advance to ensure they can accommodate all my bikes. By the way, speaking of bikes, I just got a new one recently, so I'll actually have four bikes with me on this trip - my road bike, mountain bike, commuter bike, and a new hybrid bike I just purchased.
